## Task: Support multiple run IDs in cloche poll with status display

Allow `cloche poll` to accept multiple run IDs: `cloche poll id1 id2 id3...`

## Current behavior
`cloche poll <run-id>` polls a single run and streams log output.

## New behavior
When given multiple IDs, display a compact status summary (not log output):

```
id1: running
id2: succeeded
id3: running
```

Polls until all runs reach a terminal state. Use `cloche logs` for detailed output.

Single-ID behavior remains unchanged (streams logs as today).
